9039">随后于格林尼治标准时间下午 2 点首演</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liverpools-jacaranda-club-hosts-emotional-beatles-listening-party-for-now-and-then-3529240">在利物浦的蓝花楹俱乐部举办了一场聆听派对</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-shares-new-single-were-gonna-get-there-in-the-end-3529328">Noel Gallagher 分享新单曲《We&#39;re Gonna Get There In The End》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
